---
title: Middle Eastern Inspired Cheesy Harissa Naanizza with Greek Style Salad Cheese and Apple & Baby Leaf Salad
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Middle Eastern Inspired Cheesy Harissa Naanizza in just 20-25 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
